platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In Hello Games' side-scrolling racer, you control the eponymous stunt devil as he jumps, wheelies, and backflips through a huge assortment of death-defying levels. With tricks to master, costumes to unlock, and leaderboards to conquer, Joe Danger is a wacky blast. Youll don an Elvis getup, evade flying saucers, and soar over shark tanks in increasingly treacherous tracks. After all, they dont call him Joe Danger for nothing.
